{"id":"93cd200c-6f80-4f98-a875-1fe42f7da1d1","name":"Daniel Hughes | Still Springs","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\"Outsiders spoil the order. Let's see what you've brought.\"</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Sometimes danger doesn't lurk in dark corners or the forest, but right behind you. Be careful not to become the next one to disappear in Still Springs. You think the devil has horns? Well, so did I. But I was wrong—his hair is combed, and he wears a suit and tie. The police won't help when there's a knife at your throat.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><u>Anypov</u>./<u>Fempov</u>.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Kinktober: <u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(181, 2, 2); color: inherit;\">obsession/breeding.</mark></u></em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(181, 2, 2); color: inherit;\">(swipe to see the other two scenarios)</mark></u></em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/If7qp-5qia_4kfPx4IlqX.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><strong>Dark Halloween collab by ten creators.</strong> <em>We built our own eerie universe with over twelve original characters (our sanity barely survived, lol).</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 18, 18);\"><strong>Character</strong></span>: <strong>Daniel Hughes</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 18, 18);\"><strong>Series</strong></span>: <strong>Still Springs</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 18, 18);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span>: <strong>Welco